  <title>Getting started</title>
  
  <p>This page describes how to get started using PoProofRead.</p>

  <section id="first">
    <title>Opening the podiff-file</title>
    <p>First download the file you wish to work with,
    e.g. "example.podiff". There are now three different ways that you
    open the file:</p>
    <list>
      <item><p>Start PoProofRead and use the open file dialog (Ctrl-o)</p></item>
      <item><p>Right click the example.podiff file in your file browser and find PoProofRead among the applications in the "Open with"-menu</p></item>
      <item><p>Start PoProofRead from the terminal and supply the file as a argument e.g: <cmd>poproofread-gtk example.podiff</cmd></p></item>
    </list>
  
  </section>
  
  
